preference.name: MEStudyMaturityStatusforBriefcaseExport
preference.preference_description: Defines the maturity statuses of the Study objects to use during a briefcase export of a Collaboration Context (CC). By default the value is "Approved", which means that only the studies in a CC with release status "Approved" will be exported.
